    public class JsonQueryNodeProcessorPipeline
extends org.apache.lucene.queryparser.flexible.core.processors.QueryNodeProcessorPipeline
    This pipeline has all the processors needed to process a query node tree, generated by JsonSyntaxParser, already assembled.

    The order they are assembled affects the results.

    This processor pipeline was designed to work with JsonQueryConfigHandler.

    The result query node tree can be used to build a Query object using JsonQueryTreeBuilder.

    See Also:
    JsonQueryTreeBuilder, JsonQueryConfigHandler, JsonSyntaxParser
